<p>I can&rsquo;t say that I&rsquo;m completely happy with the way emacs marks some elements, namely :</p>
<hr>
<div class="ox-hugo-toc toc local">
<ul>
<li><a href="https://emacs.dyerdwelling.family/emacs/20231209092556-emacs--redefining-mark-paragraph-and-mark-word/#mark-paragraph">mark-paragraph</a></li>
<li><a href="https://emacs.dyerdwelling.family/emacs/20231209092556-emacs--redefining-mark-paragraph-and-mark-word/#mark-word">mark-word</a></li>
</ul>
</div>
